## 2. Guest Speaker Session (30-45 Minutes)

*Guest Speaker: Arman Taheri  
Topics: DevOps & Cloud Infrastructure  
The session opened with an insightful presentation by Arman Taheri.
- DevOps: A set of practices that combines software development (Dev) and IT operations (Ops) to shorten the systems development life cycle and provide continuous high-quality delivery.
- Cloud Infrastructure: Refers to the hardware and software components (servers, storage, networks) needed for cloud computing, allowing ML models to scale and run efficiently in remote environments.

